<i>adverb</i>: 후끈 [후끈], 활활 [활활], 화끈 [화끈], 절절 [절절], 잔뜩 [잔뜩], 강렬히 [강녈히] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>후끈 [후끈]</dt><br>
<dd>1. burningly; glowingly</dd><br>
<dd>열을 받아서 갑자기 뜨거워지는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of an object becoming suddenly hot, being exposed to heat or one's face becoming suddenly hot and turning red.</dd><br>
<dd>2. burningly; intensely</dd><br>
<dd>흥분이나 긴장 등이 거세어지는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of excitement or tension, etc., becoming stronger.</dd><br>
<dt>활활 [활활]</dt><br>
<dd>1. freely; flutteringly</dd><br>
<dd>새나 곤충 등이 높이 떠서 느리게 날개를 치며 시원스럽게 나는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the motion of a bird or an insect flying freely high in the air, fluttering its wings.</dd><br>
<dd>2. fiercely; vigorously</dd><br>
<dd>불길이 세고 시원스럽게 타오르는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the motion of a fire burning strongly, wildly.</dd><br>
<dd>3. energetically; vigorously</dd><br>
<dd>부채나 손 등을 천천히 시원스럽게 흔드는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the motion of waving a hand or fan slowly, vigorously.</dd><br>
<dd>4. freely</dd><br>
<dd>옷 등을 시원스럽게 벗어 버리거나 벗기는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the motion of taking off one's own or another person's clothing freely.</dd><br>
<dd>5. burningly; fiercely; intensely</dd><br>
<dd>열기가 세게 오르는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the state of heat becoming intense.</dd><br>
<dd>6. energetically; vigorously</dd><br>
<dd>시원스럽게 씻는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the motion of washing oneself cleanly, vigorously.</dd><br>
<dt>화끈 [화끈]</dt><br>
<dd>1. burningly; glowingly</dd><br>
<dd>열을 받아서 갑자기 뜨거워지는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of an object becoming suddenly hot, being exposed to heat or one's face becoming suddenly hot and turning red.</dd><br>
<dd>2. burningly; intensely</dd><br>
<dd>흥분이나 긴장 등이 거세어지는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state of excitement or tension, etc., becoming stronger.</dd><br>
<dt>절절 [절절]</dt><br>
<dd>1. intensely; hot</dd><br>
<dd>액체 등이 높은 온도로 끓는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of a liquid, etc., boiling at a high temperature.</dd><br>
<dd>2. scorchingly</dd><br>
<dd>온도가 높아 몹시 더운 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a manner of being very hot due to a high temperature.</dd><br>
<dt>잔뜩 [잔뜩]</dt><br>
<dd>1. full; fully; to capacity</dd><br>
<dd>한계에 이를 때까지 가득.</dd><br>
<dd>To the full until something reaches the limit.</dd><br>
<dd>2. with all one's might</dd><br>
<dd>힘이 닿는 데까지 한껏.</dd><br>
<dd>To the utmost of one's ability.</dd><br>
<dd>3. heavily; extremely; intensely</dd><br>
<dd>더할 수 없이 심하게.</dd><br>
<dd>To an extreme degree.</dd><br>
<dt>강렬히 [강녈히]</dt><br>
<dd>intensely; fervently</dd><br>
<dd>매우 강하고 세게.</dd><br>
<dd>Very firmly and hard.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>